@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title Doggy - DDD Context Map (Contexts, Concepts, Events)

actor User

rectangle "User Interaction Context\n(Frontend)" as UI
rectangle "Analysis Orchestration Context\n(Backend API)" as ORCH
rectangle "Dog Recognition Context\n(In-process ML Module)" as RECOG
rectangle "Advice Generation Context\n(External LLM API)" as ADVICE

User --> UI : ImageUploaded
UI --> ORCH : AnalysisRequested\n(HTTP POST /api/dog-from-photo)
ORCH --> RECOG : DogCheckRequested\nBreedPredictionRequested
RECOG --> ORCH : DogValidated\nBreedPredictionsComputed
ORCH --> ADVICE : AdviceGenerationStarted
ADVICE --> ORCH : AdviceGenerationCompleted\nor AdviceGenerationFailed
ORCH --> UI : AnalysisCompleted\n(JSON {breed, advice, raw_predictions})
ORCH --> UI : ErrorDisplayed

note bottom of UI
Domain concepts:
- SelectedImage
- RequestState
- ApiErrorMessage

Events:
- ImageUploaded
- AnalysisRequested
- ResultDisplayed
- ErrorDisplayed
end note

note bottom of ORCH
Domain concepts:
- PhotoAnalysis (aggregate)
- BreedLabel
- RawPrediction
- AdviceText
- AnalysisResult

Events:
- PhotoReceived
- DogCheckPassed / DogCheckFailed
- BreedPredicted
- AdviceRequested / AdviceReceived
- AnalysisCompleted
end note

note bottom of RECOG
Domain concepts:
- DogValidationResult
- RawPrediction

Events:
- DogValidated
- BreedPredictionsComputed
end note

note bottom of ADVICE
Domain concepts:
- AdvicePrompt
- AdviceText

Events:
- AdviceGenerationStarted
- AdviceGenerationCompleted
- AdviceGenerationFailed
end note
@enduml
